{"date": "2026-05-07", "format": "carousel", "pillar": "vater-sohn", "image_urls": ["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d4-vater-sohn/slide-1.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d4-vater-sohn/slide-2.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d4-vater-sohn/slide-3.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d4-vater-sohn/slide-4.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d4-vater-sohn/slide-5.png"], "caption": "Dein Vater wäre nicht stolz.\n\nAber er hat's auch nie geschafft, der Mann zu werden, den du brauchst. Du wirst zu dem Mann, dem du als Kind nicht vertraut hast.\n\nWas bricht die Kette? Schreib's in die DM.\n\n—\n#mindset #mannsein #stoiker #montagsluege #generation", "status": "pending"}
{"date": "2026-05-08", "format": "carousel", "pillar": "frame-shift", "image_urls": ["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d5-frame-shift/slide-1.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d5-frame-shift/slide-2.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d5-frame-shift/slide-3.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d5-frame-shift/slide-4.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d5-frame-shift/slide-5.png"], "caption": "Disziplin ist nicht das Problem.\n\nOptionen sind das Problem. Du brauchst nicht mehr Willenskraft — du brauchst weniger Wege ins Versagen.\n\nStreich Optionen. Reduzier Friction.\n\n—\n#mindset #disziplin #mentalmodel #montagsluege #klarheit", "status": "pending"}
{"date": "2026-05-09", "format": "carousel", "pillar": "quiet-power", "image_urls": ["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d6-quiet-power/slide-1.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d6-quiet-power/slide-2.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d6-quiet-power/slide-3.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d6-quiet-power/slide-4.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d6-quiet-power/slide-5.png"], "caption": "Der gefährlichste Mann ist nicht der lauteste.\n\nEr ist der Ruhige. Der, der nichts beweisen muss. Weil er weiß, was er ist.\n\nSei unmöglich zu ignorieren. Sag wenig.\n\n—\n#mindset #stoiker #sigma #quietpower #montagsluege", "status": "pending"}
